Can I take a picture with you?

245
00:20:07,272 --> 00:20:09,412
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

246
00:20:16,897 --> 00:20:18,146
Hello, father.

247
00:20:20,694 --> 00:20:21,694
Yes.

248
00:20:23,177 --> 00:20:24,577
Yes. I'll be waiting.

249
00:20:35,514 --> 00:20:38,342
Did you wait long? My meeting went
on for longer than I thought.

250
00:20:38,654 --> 00:20:42,100
- It's fine. Please have a seat.
- Okay.

251
00:20:47,202 --> 00:20:48,602
What brings you here?

252
00:20:49,756 --> 00:20:54,350
Is there a problem between
you and Hyun-joon?

253
00:20:56,936 --> 00:20:59,686
You two must prepare for marriage.

254
00:21:00,358 --> 00:21:02,725
I don't think Hyun-joon has
the intention of rushing it.

255
00:21:04,069 --> 00:21:05,069
Why not?

256
00:21:07,092 --> 00:21:09,293
Why would you walk on eggshells around him?

257
00:21:09,990 --> 00:21:13,401
Tell your parents to set
a date for the wedding.

258
00:21:14,163 --> 00:21:17,396
Father, I actually have
something to tell you.

259
00:21:18,686 --> 00:21:20,639
Be comfortable, and tell me.

260
00:21:21,436 --> 00:21:24,818
- My family worries about Hyun-joon a lot.
- Why?

261
00:21:25,366 --> 00:21:29,170
They're not happy about him roaming
outside doing an entertainment company.

262
00:21:32,889 --> 00:21:34,404
I understand what you mean.

263
00:21:49,694 --> 00:21:51,092
I'll give you the planning office.

264
00:21:57,975 --> 00:21:59,514
Are you saying it's too excessive?

265
00:22:01,506 --> 00:22:04,553
- Then what about Hyun-sung?
- I'll move him somewhere else.

266
00:22:05,881 --> 00:22:10,811
Prepare some food. Dinner wasn't enough.

267
00:22:11,874 --> 00:22:12,874
Yes, father.

268
00:22:24,733 --> 00:22:26,553
While you're at it, be more generous.

269
00:22:28,522 --> 00:22:30,322
Give me the future strategy office.

270
00:22:33,545 --> 00:22:34,930
Then I'll come into the company.

271
00:22:36,092 --> 00:22:37,382
The future strategy office?

272
00:22:38,506 --> 00:22:42,418
Bring back the executive director Kim Ji-hoon
and vice-president Oh Jin-sung also.

273
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:46,771
They already left the company,
so why bring them back now?

274
00:22:47,170 --> 00:22:50,271
They were the people my late
grandfather had raised.

275
00:22:50,795 --> 00:22:54,201
You always thought of them as
your rivals when my grandfather

276
00:22:54,226 --> 00:22:57,685
was alive, and as soon as he
passed away, you fired them first.

277
00:22:58,897 --> 00:23:01,558
You know that very well, and yet,
you want me to call them back?

278
00:23:03,834 --> 00:23:06,114
What's going on through that mind of yours?

279
00:23:06,616 --> 00:23:09,988
Why won't you even allow Hyun-sung
near the future strategy office?

280
00:23:10,834 --> 00:23:14,193
Even if he's my son, I can't trust him yet.

281
00:23:17,170 --> 00:23:19,871
Because you're afraid, just like
how you pushed your father-in-law

282
00:23:19,896 --> 00:23:22,072
out of that seat, your son
will push you out of there?

283
00:23:24,311 --> 00:23:27,444
So you do realize you've done
something you shouldn't have,

284
00:23:28,639 --> 00:23:30,877
seeing that you can't
even trust your own sons.

285
00:23:33,288 --> 00:23:35,155
Why are you living that way?

286
00:23:35,788 --> 00:23:40,936
Because, unlike you, I wasn't
born into a rich family.

287
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:49,295
Future strategy office? Even
a passing dog would laugh.

288
00:23:51,022 --> 00:23:53,639
The deal is off the table.

289
00:23:54,522 --> 00:23:55,522
Arrogant punk.

290
00:23:56,608 --> 00:24:00,529
Who pushed you to make that deal?

291
00:24:02,264 --> 00:24:03,264
What?

292
00:24:03,428 --> 00:24:06,271
Do you remember how I told you
that was my last request?

293
00:24:08,116 --> 00:24:09,576
You said you weren't touched.

294
00:24:11,788 --> 00:24:16,357
There will be a day when you
say your last request to me.

295
00:24:17,155 --> 00:24:18,511
Don't be presumptuous.

296
00:24:18,733 --> 00:24:21,412
If you don't want to make a
last request to me, then

297
00:24:21,998 --> 00:24:24,553
drag Yoo Ji-na out of this
house with your own hands.

298
00:24:25,022 --> 00:24:28,482
- I can't do that.
- We'll see if you really can't.

299
00:24:30,709 --> 00:24:31,732
Stop right there.

300
00:24:33,272 --> 00:24:34,509
I'm not done talking yet.

301
00:24:38,631 --> 00:24:43,011
I really had no idea you
would bring my greatest ally

302
00:24:43,842 --> 00:24:47,381
into this house yourself.

303
00:24:48,373 --> 00:24:49,561
Don't be delusional.

304
00:24:50,139 --> 00:24:56,787
She's just pitying you for acting
immature for the loss of your mom.

305
00:24:57,116 --> 00:25:00,943
That's why she's my greatest ally.
Or am I missing something here?

306
00:25:02,772 --> 00:25:04,804
Although I have a useless
life, there is one thing

307
00:25:05,823 --> 00:25:08,374
that I'm good at because I'm just like you.

308
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,850
Are you done talking?

309
00:25:12,092 --> 00:25:13,334
I was talking about exercising.

310
00:25:15,366 --> 00:25:18,998
What on earth were you imagining? It
doesn't matter how uneasy you are.

311
00:25:35,638 --> 00:25:38,404
I prepared porridge, since
you'll be sleeping soon.

312
00:25:38,991 --> 00:25:39,991
Well done.

313
00:25:40,897 --> 00:25:46,193
Father, are you going to call
Hyun-joon to the planning office?

314
00:25:48,288 --> 00:25:50,288
Then Hyun-sung would be upset.

315
00:25:51,772 --> 00:25:54,909
It's work. It's nothing that
you should be concerned about.

316
00:25:55,444 --> 00:25:59,277
I apologize for saying this, but it's
rather difficult to take care of

317
00:25:59,302 --> 00:26:02,972
Yoo Ji-na while being
careful around grandmother.

318
00:26:03,672 --> 00:26:05,039
I'm grateful for that.

319
00:26:05,460 --> 00:26:11,015
When I suggested you bring Yoo Ji-na to
the annex, I only thought of your sake,

320
00:26:11,499 --> 00:26:13,812
but grandmother is making
me walk on eggshells.

321
00:26:14,343 --> 00:26:15,343
Sweetie.

322
00:26:15,929 --> 00:26:16,929
Yes, father.

323
00:26:17,234 --> 00:26:18,632
I would like to eat in silence.

324
00:26:19,836 --> 00:26:20,836
I apologize.

325
00:26:21,890 --> 00:26:23,090
I'll be going now.

326
00:26:29,593 --> 00:26:31,296
Hello, grandmother.

327
00:26:31,500 --> 00:26:34,819
- Bring tea to my room.
- Okay.

328
00:27:02,578 --> 00:27:04,063
I prepared Chinese quince tea.

329
00:27:06,968 --> 00:27:11,937
I'll be going out now to
clean up father's dishes.

330
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:13,140
Stay down.

331
00:27:14,109 --> 00:27:16,444
Is there something you
would like to tell me?

332
00:27:35,078 --> 00:27:36,273
Why are you so pale?

333
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,720
I think she heard me.

334
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,000
Who heard what?

335
00:27:44,858 --> 00:27:50,607
I was the one who first suggested your
father bring Yoo Ji-na to the annex.

336
00:27:51,406 --> 00:27:55,444
- What?
- I think the old hag heard that.

337
00:27:58,257 --> 00:27:59,999
Why did you do such a fearless thing?

338
00:28:01,547 --> 00:28:04,554
I should've known ever since
you mentioned a total war.

339
00:28:05,015 --> 00:28:08,695
Then what was I supposed to do? I can't
even have your child. It looked like I

340
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:12,353
was about to be kicked out after serving
all the bragging women in this house.

341
00:28:13,406 --> 00:28:14,406
Goodness.

342
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:18,273
Your father told Hyun-joon to
come into the planning office.

343
00:28:19,179 --> 00:28:21,246
- He did?
- I heard him myself.

344
00:28:24,843 --> 00:28:27,269
He used you for all the dirty
work so far, and then at the

345
00:28:27,294 --> 00:28:29,843
most crucial moment, he's giving
everything to his eldest son.

346
00:28:30,398 --> 00:28:31,881
How could he do such a thing?

347
00:28:32,273 --> 00:28:34,554
- What did Hyun-joon say?
- I couldn't hear that.

348
00:28:35,797 --> 00:28:38,648
I never knew your father would do that.

349
00:28:39,304 --> 00:28:41,522
How could you trust him in the first place?

350
00:28:43,515 --> 00:28:44,657
He was always like that.

351
00:28:45,856 --> 00:28:48,312
He uses you as if he'll have
your back anytime, but when the

352
00:28:49,309 --> 00:28:52,129
situation changes, he'll ignore
you like nothing happened.

353
00:28:54,590 --> 00:28:56,473
That's why I told you to know your place.

354
00:28:56,716 --> 00:28:58,973
Please don't say such a thing to me!

355
00:29:01,223 --> 00:29:02,301
What will you do now?

356
00:29:02,450 --> 00:29:06,621
Yoo Ji-na, you dare ignored my words?

357
00:29:16,848 --> 00:29:17,915
Is that a snack?

358
00:29:25,489 --> 00:29:26,926
I have something to inquire you.

359
00:29:27,293 --> 00:29:28,465
"Inquire?"

360
00:29:29,278 --> 00:29:32,137
Since you speak like that, it seems
like I became your mother-in-law.

361
00:29:32,333 --> 00:29:35,051
Then what should I do to
make you feel comfortable?

362
00:29:36,122 --> 00:29:39,472
Just comfortably call me
"Ji-na," and when we talk,

363
00:29:39,497 --> 00:29:43,169
please don't speak like we're
filming a historical drama.

364
00:29:44,537 --> 00:29:45,537
Should I?

365
00:29:46,826 --> 00:29:53,021
Then Ji-na, did you tell my father-in-law
to bring Hyun-joon to the planning office?

366
00:29:53,466 --> 00:29:55,133
- Planning office?
- Yes.

367
00:29:57,256 --> 00:29:58,903
How would I know that that is?

368
00:29:59,623 --> 00:30:04,036
All I told him was to get
along with his eldest son.

369
00:30:05,795 --> 00:30:07,302
I thought I told you not to do that.

370
00:30:08,607 --> 00:30:09,764
"I thought I told you?"

371
00:30:13,865 --> 00:30:16,183
I told you to speak comfortably,
but since you suddenly

372
00:30:16,208 --> 00:30:18,189
regarded me so casually,
I'm getting flustered.

373
00:30:20,216 --> 00:30:23,528
It's wise for you to not do what
I tell you not to do, Ji-na.

374
00:30:30,412 --> 00:30:34,661
You're just old. You're not
the smart style at all.

375
00:30:36,459 --> 00:30:37,459
Is that so?

376
00:30:37,685 --> 00:30:39,068
Let me make myself clear.

377
00:30:40,521 --> 00:30:46,009
There's no one in this house you can
treat so carelessly, including me.

378
00:30:58,795 --> 00:30:59,997
This is delicious.

379
00:31:01,584 --> 00:31:05,013
If you want to fulfill your goal before
my father-in-law's love cooks for you,

380
00:31:06,099 --> 00:31:08,164
you must refrain from acting so rashly.

381
00:31:09,943 --> 00:31:11,200
What's my goal?

382
00:31:11,646 --> 00:31:15,943
To stay in this house and get
closer to Park Hyun-joon.

383
00:31:19,497 --> 00:31:24,885
Do you now realize there isn't anyone you
can treat carelessly in this family, Ji-na?

384
00:31:33,709 --> 00:31:35,575
How dare the likes of you think I'm easy?

385
00:31:46,028 --> 00:31:49,677
I heard your father called you to the
planning office, but you had rejected him.

386
00:31:50,912 --> 00:31:52,739
Isn't the planning office
excessive for you?

387
00:31:52,900 --> 00:31:55,153
Do you think he'll give me
such a position for free?

388
00:31:55,871 --> 00:31:56,943
What do you mean?

389
00:31:58,107 --> 00:32:00,794
He wants me to accept Yoo Ji-na.

390
00:32:01,263 --> 00:32:03,068
- Then accept her.
- What?

391
00:32:03,411 --> 00:32:05,083
Is that more important than our marriage?

392
00:32:05,170 --> 00:32:08,497
You want me to easily accept her?

393
00:32:08,802 --> 00:32:11,622
- What's hard about that?
- And yet, you say you love me?

394
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:15,560
I told you I'm doing
this because I love you.

395
00:32:15,701 --> 00:32:19,066
I don't want that kind of love.

396
00:32:20,521 --> 00:32:23,802
I refuse love that suffocates me.

397
00:32:24,982 --> 00:32:28,568
I'd rather not get married than
marry a woman who suffocates me.

398
00:32:30,959 --> 00:32:32,692
Do you have another woman?

399
00:32:33,857 --> 00:32:37,302
- Not yet.
- Not... yet?

400
00:32:40,349 --> 00:32:41,349
Hyun-joon.

401
00:33:27,490 --> 00:33:28,490
Kyung-soo...

402
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:39,630
Welcome. Sit anywhere you like.

403
00:33:43,045 --> 00:33:44,045
Kyung-soo.

404
00:33:59,209 --> 00:34:00,209
Are you...

405
00:34:02,529 --> 00:34:03,529
Hae-dang?

406
00:34:05,466 --> 00:34:07,693
What happened?

407
00:34:32,412 --> 00:34:33,412
You look...

408
00:34:36,841 --> 00:34:38,638
just the way I imagined you would.

409
00:34:41,341 --> 00:34:46,239
You're the first one I wanted
to see after the surgery.

410
00:34:48,248 --> 00:34:49,715
Did you get the surgery?

411
00:34:51,881 --> 00:34:53,458
I really missed you.

412
00:34:55,631 --> 00:34:56,631
Kyung-soo.

413
00:35:14,052 --> 00:35:15,583
Have you been well?

414
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:42,447
I've been waiting a long
time for a cornea donor,

415
00:35:43,162 --> 00:35:45,411
but I never thought the
opportunity would come to me.

416
00:35:45,943 --> 00:35:48,036
So you had become blind
after a car accident.

417
00:35:48,895 --> 00:35:52,778
Fortunately, I'm not experiencing a rejection,
so my vision is slowly getting better.

418
00:35:54,115 --> 00:35:57,622
Of course, I have a long way to go, but I
don't think there will be any problems.

419
00:35:58,959 --> 00:36:01,825
I'm very happy for you.

420
00:36:04,146 --> 00:36:10,654
- Can I touch your face?
- My face?

421
00:36:27,193 --> 00:36:28,326
It really is you.

422
00:36:30,326 --> 00:36:31,739
The one I had missed so much.

423
00:36:41,317 --> 00:36:43,333
You had such beautiful eyes.

424
00:36:45,216 --> 00:36:48,949
They're much more bigger and beautiful
than I had imagined them to be.

425
00:36:51,318 --> 00:36:52,560
I missed you.

426
00:36:55,435 --> 00:36:58,716
You came back.

427
00:38:30,549 --> 00:38:32,373
(Choi Kyung-ae)

428
00:38:41,662 --> 00:38:45,724
If I somehow end up leaving
this world, please give

429
00:38:45,749 --> 00:38:49,420
the enclosed envelope to
my son Park Hyun-joon.

430
00:38:50,365 --> 00:38:52,652
No matter what happens, you
must give it to him yourself.

431
00:39:02,513 --> 00:39:06,208
- Why are you coming home now?
- I had a drink with my co-workers.

432
00:39:07,631 --> 00:39:11,286
- Come here for a moment.
- Why?

433
00:39:13,216 --> 00:39:15,427
From now on, wear this.

434
00:39:17,615 --> 00:39:19,747
- What's this?
- Open it if you're so curious.

435
00:39:25,943 --> 00:39:29,246
Gosh. I can't wear this. It's suffocating.

436
00:39:29,271 --> 00:39:31,318
You must bear with it even
though it's suffocating.

437
00:39:31,343 --> 00:39:33,833
These are for young boys!
Just look at this!

438
00:39:33,858 --> 00:39:37,130
It's not the time for you to
complain about that right now.

439
00:39:37,155 --> 00:39:38,155
Gosh.

440
00:39:39,474 --> 00:39:45,255
Mom, I ate dinner, but why am I hungry?
Make me ramen.

441
00:39:46,934 --> 00:39:50,200
Is eating all you think about when
you can't even earn your keep?

442
00:39:50,310 --> 00:39:54,778
- Forget it then.
- Take this with you!

443
00:39:55,279 --> 00:39:58,364
Gosh! How do you expect me to wear this?

444
00:40:00,731 --> 00:40:02,131
Why is this so tight?

445
00:40:10,177 --> 00:40:11,177
Did you wash?

446
00:40:12,381 --> 00:40:13,685
Can't you tell?

447
00:40:14,146 --> 00:40:17,184
Did you wash properly? Did you just
spray yourself with water again?

448
00:40:17,248 --> 00:40:20,599
Check the smell then. Here.
Don't I smell like soap?

449
00:40:25,527 --> 00:40:32,307
How could you smell like an old man
even when you're not forty yet?

450
00:40:32,584 --> 00:40:35,110
I don't smell like that. I smell fine.

451
00:40:38,154 --> 00:40:39,443
What are you looking for?

452
00:40:40,051 --> 00:40:41,051
Is it this?

453
00:40:44,029 --> 00:40:45,429
Yes. This is cologne.

454
00:40:46,935 --> 00:40:49,068
Goodness!

455
00:40:50,177 --> 00:40:52,232
What are you doing right now?

456
00:40:53,013 --> 00:40:55,227
Your wife doesn't like
you because you smell!

457
00:40:55,252 --> 00:40:58,841
How could you spray cologne
like it's mosquito repellent?

458
00:41:05,420 --> 00:41:10,051
- I had something to tell him. Good night.
- Good night.

459
00:41:16,271 --> 00:41:22,739
- What's this smell? My head hurts.
Did you spray cologne?
- N-No...

460
00:41:31,732 --> 00:41:34,724
Are you going to sleep in
Hoon's room tonight, too?

461
00:41:36,818 --> 00:41:37,880
Go away!

462
00:41:38,763 --> 00:41:40,841
Gosh! Why did you put on so much cologne?

463
00:41:44,716 --> 00:41:49,357
Honey, I love you.

464
00:41:50,443 --> 00:41:52,286
You what?

465
00:41:53,615 --> 00:41:57,060
I said I love you.

466
00:41:58,052 --> 00:41:59,052
Say it again.

467
00:42:00,365 --> 00:42:05,341
Yes, well, I love you, Jung Hae-jin...

468
00:42:13,051 --> 00:42:19,885
Are you teasing me? How dare you say
you love me. Am I that easy to you?

469
00:42:19,982 --> 00:42:25,310
No, no, no. I'm really sorry.

470
00:42:25,763 --> 00:42:29,130
I dare you to say such nonsense again.

471
00:42:38,248 --> 00:42:39,989
What a temper!

472
00:42:41,396 --> 00:42:43,677
I won't freaking love you! I won't!

473
00:42:44,638 --> 00:42:47,060
My goodness.

474
00:42:49,279 --> 00:42:52,357
Hey, she's taking her pajamas
and going into that room again.

475
00:42:52,701 --> 00:42:56,083
- Do something.
- What can I do?

476
00:42:56,709 --> 00:43:01,285
I said one thing, and she got angry.
She was glaring wildly at me.

477
00:43:02,823 --> 00:43:05,107
- What did you say to her?
- That I love her.

478
00:43:05,748 --> 00:43:09,364
- What did she say?
- That if I say nonsense
like that again, she'll kill me.

479
00:43:10,396 --> 00:43:11,463
She'll kill you?

480
00:43:14,326 --> 00:43:16,393
How did you get into this mess?

481
00:43:17,037 --> 00:43:20,372
You said you love your wife, and all she
says is that you're saying nonsense!

482
00:43:20,397 --> 00:43:25,841
I don't know! Do you think I care?
I feel comfortable sleeping alone!

483
00:43:26,076 --> 00:43:29,310
Already? How could you
feel comfortable already?

484
00:43:29,584 --> 00:43:32,962
- Stop it, and just get out.
- How old are you? How can

485
00:43:32,987 --> 00:43:36,002
you already feel comfortable
about sleeping alone?

486
00:43:36,027 --> 00:43:37,427
I can't control that!

487
00:43:39,279 --> 00:43:44,177
You fool! What did you do
with all the food you ate?

488
00:43:45,060 --> 00:43:47,982
You need to get hit by me, too!

489
00:44:21,795 --> 00:44:23,896
Mom! Mom! Mom!

490
00:44:25,787 --> 00:44:28,950
Give me my life back. Give me my life back!

491
00:44:29,834 --> 00:44:33,607
What's this? You scared me.

492
00:44:34,568 --> 00:44:37,083
You said you would put your
life on the stake and love me.

493
00:44:37,413 --> 00:44:41,403
You said you would kill me if I
said I loved you one more time.

494
00:44:41,638 --> 00:44:45,497
Every night, you would cry and
whine in front of my house!

495
00:44:46,396 --> 00:44:48,286
You said you would die
if I didn't marry you!

496
00:44:48,802 --> 00:44:52,114
You put on all kinds of show
on the rooftop of the school!

497
00:44:53,607 --> 00:44:56,989
I got it, so please let me sleep.

498
00:44:57,014 --> 00:45:01,238
Honey, all I want to do is get some sleep.

499
00:45:01,263 --> 00:45:04,224
I'm so angry that I'm
about to lose my mind.

500
00:45:04,990 --> 00:45:07,911
Will the world fall apart if you
don't get some sleep? Will it?

501
00:45:09,584 --> 00:45:11,942
- How should I give you your life back?
- What?

502
00:45:12,044 --> 00:45:15,943
So how do I give you your life back?

503
00:45:15,968 --> 00:45:18,318
How can you say that?

504
00:45:19,474 --> 00:45:21,982
If I say something, you throw
a fit because I talked.

505
00:45:22,756 --> 00:45:25,823
If I keep my mouth shut, you throw
a fit because I kept silent.

506
00:45:26,677 --> 00:45:30,466
Gosh! Fine! Do whatever you want!

507
00:45:31,450 --> 00:45:33,380
I'm so sleepy.

508
00:45:41,568 --> 00:45:43,955
Do you think I wasted my nights studying so

509
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:46,530
that I could be a
valedictorian in high school?

510
00:45:47,755 --> 00:45:51,303
