something urgent came up, so I can't make it.

660
00:59:28,849 --> 00:59:31,646
I see. Are you asking
me to perform instead?

661
00:59:35,691 --> 00:59:38,582
Ask your friends. I told you
I don't do those things.

662
00:59:39,006 --> 00:59:42,997
I can't recommend just anyone. It's for a
wealthy family, so they'll pay you well.

663
00:59:43,873 --> 00:59:46,122
You know GR Group, don't you?

664
01:00:12,537 --> 01:00:13,537
Welcome.

665
01:00:15,677 --> 01:00:20,318
It's nice to meet you. I selected the
songs I'm going to play at the party.

666
01:00:21,021 --> 01:00:24,286
I'm glad you came. Are you a music student?

667
01:00:24,646 --> 01:00:28,138
No. She had an emergency,
so I came on her behalf.

668
01:00:28,443 --> 01:00:29,443
I see.

669
01:00:31,123 --> 01:00:33,794
It doesn't matter anyways.
Please take a seat.

670
01:00:35,529 --> 01:00:36,763
Yes, you can sit here.

671
01:00:41,756 --> 01:00:44,341
- What's your name?
- Yoon Sung-ha.

672
01:00:44,950 --> 01:00:48,286
Please wait a moment, Sung-ha.
I'll get you something to drink.

673
01:01:34,404 --> 01:01:35,404
Be careful!

674
01:01:38,888 --> 01:01:40,200
Get up. Are you okay?

675
01:01:45,373 --> 01:01:46,450
Who are you?

676
01:01:48,193 --> 01:01:50,864
I'll be the one playing the
piano during the party.

677
01:01:51,396 --> 01:01:52,724
Oh, I see.

678
01:01:56,334 --> 01:01:59,786
But I think I've seen you somewhere before.

679
01:02:02,599 --> 01:02:04,935
Your face looks familiar.

680
01:02:07,623 --> 01:02:08,756
Oh, that's right!

681
01:02:09,545 --> 01:02:11,024
The cafe in Hae-dang's neighborhood?

682
01:02:13,584 --> 01:02:15,224
