686
01:02:24,201 --> 01:02:27,239
I thought you had special piano skills.

687
01:02:28,490 --> 01:02:30,708
Thank you for thinking that way.

688
01:02:31,584 --> 01:02:34,083
He's blind.

689
01:02:36,584 --> 01:02:37,584
Bye.

690
01:02:42,826 --> 01:02:45,513
Should I help you?

691
01:02:50,748 --> 01:02:51,748
No, thank you.

692
01:03:21,948 --> 01:03:24,631
(You Are Too Much)

693
01:03:24,708 --> 01:03:26,625
- Do you live here?
